{"tid":1645383,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"失蹤女義士陳彥霖已經死左","createTime":"2019-10-11T01:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T03:54:12.000Z","uid":222614,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b9a3e9d801e87801bcfc4ee4edbeaa7d6eb5b3","tid":1645383,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:07:33.000Z","msg":"網上流傳一則15歲失蹤少女陳彥霖的尋人啟事，她自9月19日失蹤多天仍未尋回，網民紛表憂心，近日網上有留言指她「已經死咗，變咗浮屍」。警方接受《蘋果》查詢時證實，9月22日在油塘魔鬼山一帶海面發現一具全裸女浮屍，調查後相信為15歲陳姓失蹤女童，但未有進一步確認浮屍是否陳彥霖。彥霖多個身邊人向《蘋果》確認，警方發現的浮屍就是彥霖，不過她本身是游泳健將，生前又經常「發夢」，多次參與反修例示威，憂慮死因有可疑。職訓局（VTC）確認陳彥霖是該校學生，並證實其死訊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06zVukv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06zVukv.jpg&h=a3eb75de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191011/60139820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191011%2F60139820&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=77fd1b68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191011%2F60139820&h=aabbc9d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191011/60139820</a>"},{"pid":"1ec84598234288d510ac3e5cd35774b34e9b86c6","tid":1645383,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:08:30.000Z","msg":"唔知佢有無曾經被捕"},{"pid":"a754e7b371cc5cb69d59e2afb563903550d16ad0","tid":1645383,"uid":101812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:08:51.000Z","msg":"香港人<br />\n10月日程表出左啦 你又出左未啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ajMgZVv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FajMgZVv.jpg&h=62a2e530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<i